// Signing.xcconfig
//
// Copy this file to Signing.xcconfig (same directory) and set your
// Apple Developer Team ID below. Signing.xcconfig is gitignored so
// each contributor keeps their own team on their machine without
// committing it.
//
// To find your team ID:
//   Xcode > Settings > Accounts > (your Apple ID) > Manage Certificates
//   Or: System Settings > Apple ID, then look for the membership details.
//   A free personal Apple ID also works for on-device development.
//
// Uncomment and fill in:
// DEVELOPMENT_TEAM = YOUR10CHARID
